## Practice Questions

**Question 1**  
Expand and simplify $$ (a + 3)(2a - 3) $$.  


**Question 2**  
Expand and simplify $$ (x + 2y)(3x - y) $$.  


**Question 3**  
Expand and simplify the following expressions:  
(a) $$ 5(x - 5) - 2x(5 - x) $$  

(b) $$ (3x - 2y)^2 $$  

(c) $$ (2p + 5q)(2p - 5q) $$  


**Question 4**  
Expand and simplify $$ (x + 4)(x^2 + x - 2) $$.  


**Question 5**  
Expand and simplify $$ (m^2 - 9)(2m + 1) $$.  


**Question 6**  
Expand and simplify $$ (2x - 1)(3x + 2) $$.  


**Question 7**  
Expand and simplify $$ (3x - 2)(x + 1) $$.  


**Question 8**  
Expand and simplify $$ (-c - 2d)(2c - 5d + 3) $$.  


**Question 9**  
Expand and simplify $$ 5x(x - 9y) $$.  


**Question 10**  
Expand and simplify $$ (5 - 2x)(3x + 1) $$.  


**Question 11**  
Expand $$ (2a + b)(2a - b) $$.  


**Question 12**  
Expand and simplify $$ (7y + 3x)(x - 2y) $$.  


**Question 13**  
Expand and simplify $$ (2x - 7)(3x + 1) $$.  


## Practice Questions and Solutions

**Question 1**  
Expand and simplify $$ (a + 3)(2a - 3) $$.  
Distributed: $$ 2a^2 + 6a - 3a - 9 $$  
Simplified: $$ 2a^2 + 3a - 9 $$

**Question 2**  
Expand and simplify $$ (x + 2y)(3x - y) $$.  
Distributed: $$ 3x^2 + 6xy - xy - 2y^2 $$  
Simplified: $$ 3x^2 + 5xy - 2y^2 $$

**Question 3**  
Expand and simplify the following expressions:  
(a) $$ 5(x - 5) - 2x(5 - x) $$  
Distributed: $$ 5x - 25 - 10x + 2x^2 $$  
Simplified: $$ 2x^2 - 5x - 25 $$  
(b) $$ (3x - 2y)^2 $$  
Distributed: $$ 9x^2 - 6xy - 6xy + 4y^2 $$  
Simplified: $$ 9x^2 - 12xy + 4y^2 $$  
(c) $$ (2p + 5q)(2p - 5q) $$  
Distributed: $$ 4p^2 - 10pq + 10pq - 25q^2 $$  
Simplified: $$ 4p^2 - 25q^2 $$

**Question 4**  
Expand and simplify $$ (x + 4)(x^2 + x - 2) $$.  
Distributed: $$ x^3 + x^2 - 2x + 4x^2 + 4x - 8 $$  
Simplified: $$ x^3 + 5x^2 + 2x - 8 $$

**Question 5**  
Expand and simplify $$ (m^2 - 9)(2m + 1) $$.  
Distributed: $$ 2m^3 + m^2 - 18m - 9 $$  
Simplified: $$ 2m^3 + m^2 - 18m - 9 $$

**Question 6**  
Expand and simplify $$ (2x - 1)(3x + 2) $$.  
Distributed: $$ 6x^2 + 4x - 3x - 2 $$  
Simplified: $$ 6x^2 + x - 2 $$

**Question 7**  
Expand and simplify $$ (3x - 2)(x + 1) $$.  
Distributed: $$ 3x^2 + 3x - 2x - 2 $$  
Simplified: $$ 3x^2 + x - 2 $$

**Question 8**  
Expand and simplify $$ (-c - 2d)(2c - 5d + 3) $$.  
Distributed: $$ -2c^2 + 5cd - 3c - 4cd + 10d^2 - 6d $$  
Simplified: $$ -2c^2 + cd - 3c + 10d^2 - 6d $$

**Question 9**  
Expand and simplify $$ 5x(x - 9y) $$.  
Distributed: $$ 5x^2 - 45xy $$  
Simplified: $$ 5x^2 - 45xy $$

**Question 10**  
Expand and simplify $$ (5 - 2x)(3x + 1) $$.  
Distributed: $$ 15x + 5 - 6x^2 - 2x $$  
Simplified: $$ -6x^2 + 13x + 5 $$

**Question 11**  
Expand $$ (2a + b)(2a - b) $$.  
Distributed: $$ 4a^2 - 2ab + 2ab - b^2 $$  
Simplified: $$ 4a^2 - b^2 $$

**Question 12**  
Expand and simplify $$ (7y + 3x)(x - 2y) $$.  
Distributed: $$ 7xy - 14y^2 + 3x^2 - 6xy $$  
Simplified: $$ 3x^2 + xy - 14y^2 $$

**Question 13**  
Expand and simplify $$ (2x - 7)(3x + 1) $$.  
Distributed: $$ 6x^2 + 2x - 21x - 7 $$  
Simplified: $$ 6x^2 - 19x - 7 $$

